Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:03.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(262,386)\a1\fs20\bord0\shad0\b0\fscx100\fsp0\fnShinGoPro-Medium}(Miki Matsuhashi)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.42,0:00:04.27,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Even fate can be used as a hint for reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:06.30,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Seeing through the most mysterious cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:08.05,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}An odd member in a sealed-room situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:10.12,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What will happen to Conan and Haibara now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:11.74,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.70,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.01,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:46.50,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Haibara and I boarded a bus with Dr. Agasa and the Detective Boys
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.50,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}on our way to get in some spring skiing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.95,0:01:56.09,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}On the way, Araide-{\i1}sensei{\i0} and\NJodie-{\i1}sensei{\i0} also boarded the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:02:00.00,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Suddenly, Haibara became scared.\NShe just wasn't herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:10.70,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Then two men in ski gear\Nboarded the bus and hijacked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:15.63,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I hid and tried to contact the police, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You little twerp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:24.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, twerp...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:28.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try anything funny again,\Nyou're really gonna get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:31.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Damn! He took my phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:36.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But it's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:38.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He made a beeline for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}but he couldn't have seen what I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:43.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Which means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:46.21,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}They've got an accomplice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:50.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}One of the three people who can see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But how did that person contact him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:03:00.69,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and tell him what I was doing\Nwithout letting anyone else know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:03.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What method are they using?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:19.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haibara, do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:21.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:32.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything foolish, Cool Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:38.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have a good chance soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:42.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't have to be so scared. It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:45.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name, Little Red Riding Hood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:55.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name, Little Red Riding Hood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:02.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a stranger, we just happen to be sitting next to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:05.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really scared, so I think we should leave her alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:06.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm sorry!\N- You over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jodie-{\i1}sensei{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:15.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do anything to irritate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:17.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:29.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someone's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}On this bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}One of {\i1}them{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:43.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:45.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I still haven't figured out who the other hijacker is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Until I come up with a plan to stop this gang,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't do anything about the men in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's one of those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}And the most likely suspect...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}is the guy who's been coughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:08.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That could be his way of signalling the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.97,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(316,350)}Shuichi Akai\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:12.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But the Doc's been coughing too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and their coughing sounds about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Speaking of sounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:21.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}there's that woman's gum-chewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:25.65,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(316,350)}Miharu Tomino\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:25.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's not as loud as the coughing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Those guys were standing at the front of the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:33.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}There's no way they could've\Nheard her chewing gum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That leaves that guy with the hearing aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}If that hearing aid were a wireless microphone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:44.84,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,750)\pos(322,350)}Yasuhiko Machida\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:44.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}he could be using it to talk to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:48.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But neither of the hijackers\Nhave anything in their ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:52.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}And surely people would\Nnotice him talking to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:57.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The hijackers keep checking\Nthe rearview mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:03.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to pull?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:06.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's only cough medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:07.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:10.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someone alerted the hijackers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:13.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Damn! How is it being done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}How are they communicating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:20.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we've been waiting for your call, Yashima-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:22.95,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So how are things on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:27.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's fine. I managed to lose the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:31.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll meet at the\Nusual place in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, driver,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:37.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,get on the Shuto Expressway,\Nthen head for the Chuo Expressway!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:45.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get to the Kobotoke Tunnel, slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:49.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:51.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll release the passengers,\Njust like we promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! The geek in the glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:09.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the guy in the back with the cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, get up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:17.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter? Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:20.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I see. So that's what they're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:30.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I've figured out who their other partner is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:33.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and how they intend to escape from this bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Do you have any lipstick?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:19.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Now to use this badge and get those guys to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:32.53,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Where can your lipstick bring us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.40,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Show me your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.92,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Cool Guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sato here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:52.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus is currently on the Chuo Expressway heading toward Otsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:55.05,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}We'll reach the Kobotoke Tunnel soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:59.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep following them. Don't lose sight of the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:00.41,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:04.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus has to be running out of gas by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:09.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll probably free the first three hostages when they stop for fuel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact the Yamanashi Prefectural Police for backup
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:17.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and ask them to place plainclothes detectives at every parking area along the route!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:18.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:23.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready to storm the bus\Nthe instant they open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:27.07,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Inspector! The bus is slowing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:28.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:32.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to enter the Kobotoke Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:47.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:49.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Put on this ski gear and sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:53.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't forget the hats and goggles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:02.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna buy us some time by posing as us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:09.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,while we disguise ourselves as two of the released passengers and make our getaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:15.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Once this is over, the other passengers will be able to clear your names.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:20.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And as to whether our escape is successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that, driver, is up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:26.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get off the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:29.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,start driving away to distract the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:32.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To make sure you play along,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:34.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to take a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You, the woman in the back chewing gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:54.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:10.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, when we get to the end of the tunnel, speed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:14.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lose the cops, then pull over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:19.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After we get off, drive until you run out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:23.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, I'll blow this woman's face off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:24.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}No, that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:31.18,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}She's no hostage. She's one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:35.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}After the three of them get off the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:38.86,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}they'll detonate the explosives in these bags,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:41.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}killing us all so we can't testify as to what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:45.51,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:51.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}They're going to pose as hostages,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}have the police take them into protective custody,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:56.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}then feed them a story about fictitious hijackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:02.55,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The police think there were only two hijackers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:08.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}so they just need to say that there was a struggle between the passengers and the hijackers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:11.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and the police will assume that the explosives went off early,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:14.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and the hijackers died in the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:21.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That means that the bodies of Araide-{\i1}sensei{\i0} and the guy with the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:25.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}will be found in the wreckage, wearing ski gear,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:28.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and the police will think {\i1}they{\i0} were the hijackers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}They waited for the bus to get into the tunnel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:34.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}so no one would see them making their decoys dress up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:37.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But this darkness works to my advantage too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:46.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Detective Boys badges...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- C-Conan?\N- Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:52.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Ears! Ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.72,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:57.15,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Do exactly what I'm about to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:59.55,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Don't worry. The inside of the bus is dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.29,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}They're so sure their plan will work, their guard is down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:06.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When the bus comes out of the tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's game on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, step on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try anything funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:33.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow orders and you'll all be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:34.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're full of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're planning to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:41.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why you're letting us see your faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:45.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, they're planning to kill us all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:46.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with this bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:51.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You twerp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:52.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shut you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:01.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? What's that red graffiti?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:20.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:26.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let go, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:27.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:54.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:04.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Araide-{\i1}sensei{\i0}! Grab that lady's arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:09.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The watch she's wearing is the switch to detonate the bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:14.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Twerp, you just made a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:31.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The airbrake going off knocked me off balance...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:35.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't dick me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what gives? The trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:44.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:50.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know you can set the safety lock on a Tokarev
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:53.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by lifting the firing hammer and stopping it midway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:58.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've learned how to use your piece before trying to hijack a bus with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:02.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the? Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:06.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:10.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:14.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A secret makes a woman woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:20.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:27.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta run for it! We've gotta get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:30.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When the airbrake went off, my wristwatch must've hit something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:32.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bomb's been activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:35.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's less than a minute before the bus blows!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:43.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, the bus is in the area of the Kobotoke Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:45.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've come to a sudden stop and aren't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:47.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:49.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we storm the bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:52.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for your backup to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:08.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bomb those hijackers brought on the bus is gonna go off in less than 20 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:10.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:14.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop the cars still in the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:16.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}, you cover the opposite lane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:18.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you, help lead the passengers away from the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:19.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:25.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where's Haibara-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:26.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:28.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:30.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Don't tell me she...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This is the best way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:41.06,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}If I make it out of this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:45.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'll have to face {\i1}her{\i0} during the questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:49.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But if I disappear now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:53.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}then there'd be nothing left to link those guys with the organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I've always known...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I knew that from the moment I ran away from the organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:05.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}there'd never be a place for me anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm such a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:09.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:48.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:56.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:58.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take her to a hospital with the Doc and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:03.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can answer all the police's questions by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:06.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:11.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:17.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't run away...from your own destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:23.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now hurry and get them to a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:33.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Cool Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:39.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking the window like that and rescuing the girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:41.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that was so James Bond!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jodie-{\i1}sensei{\i0}, you're more like 007 than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You tripped the hijacker and pretended to apologize,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but actually, you activated the safety on the Tokarev, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:55.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:58.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It went exactly like in the movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:00.53,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:07.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you know she was part of their gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:09.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the bubbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bubbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:15.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was chewing bubble gum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:17.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how she was signalling the hijackers through the rearview mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:20.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as to which passenger was acting suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:23.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bubble would break,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the hand she used to pull the gum off would show the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:30.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the number of fingers she used would show which seat the passenger was in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:36.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how did you know her watch would set off the bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:41.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was wearing a watch that was stopped at 1:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:42.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That made me suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:45.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so mad though!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:48.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Their boss got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:49.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:57.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the police wouldn't free him without a plan to recapture him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be back behind bars soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:02.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, all passengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have some questions to ask all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:06.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so please get into the cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:12.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all scratched up.\NAre you sure you're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:20.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought! You're badly wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a very reckless boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:24.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Araide-{\i1}sensei{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:27.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get you treated before you talk to the police, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:28.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:04.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it hurt, Haibara-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:07.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your leg's all bloody.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.54,0:23:10.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. It's not my blood anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:13.28,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.48,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He smeared his own blood on me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.48,0:23:19.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}so that I'd be taken away from there...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:24.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It seems you've repaid your debt to me, Kudo-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:28.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get in quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:34.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to continue my assignment\Ndue to an unexpected accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:36.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The target did not appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.13,0:23:38.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll resume my investigation later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.75,0:23:39.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:24:09.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(134,104)\fnSegoe\fscx105\fs28\fsp1\shad0\bord0\alpha&H1F&}NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.20,0:23:56.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he fell from his own apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:24:00.07,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Did he slip while going to and from the balcony?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:04.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Huh? I think the doorbell's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:07.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Yoshimura-{\i1}san{\i0}'s death was no accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.95,0:24:09.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He was murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:15.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(320,56)}Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:20.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Sandals
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.66,0:24:25.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,382)\b0\fs30\bord0\shad0}Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.63,0:24:22.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The next episode will air on May 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.21,0:24:25.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}There's a break next week, so watch the Conan movie instead!
